title: Plan to launch six new products under Renault-Nissan alliance is on schedule: Official
description: Renault India is progressing on schedule with its plan to roll out six new products, including two electric vehicles, under the Renault-Nissan alliance. The company has invested 70-80% of the committed Rs 5,300 crore so far. New limited edition variants of existing models have also been launched, available on a first-come-first-served basis.
